IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. COND-LOOP.

DATA DIVISION.
01 X PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 Y PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 COUNTER PICTURE IS 9(3).
01 BYVAR PICTURE IS 9(3).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 10 TO X
    MOVE 20 TO Y
    IF X < Y THEN
        MOVE 2 TO COUNTER
    ELSE
        MOVE 3 TO COUNTER
    END

    LOOP VARYING COUNTER FROM 1 TO 5 BY 1
        DISPLAY COUNTER
    END

    LOOP WHILE X < 12
        ADD 1 TO X
    END

    LOOP UNTIL Y = 22
        ADD 1 TO Y
    END

    SUBTRACT 1 FROM 2 GIVING BYVAR
    LOOP VARYING COUNTER FROM 5 TO 1 BY BYVAR
        DISPLAY COUNTER
    END.
